- Use DEFINE_SIMPLE_DEV_PM_OPS instead of SIMPLE_DEV_PM_OPS.
- Use pm_sleep_ptr instead of CONFIG_PM_SLEEP.
- Change the return data type of pci1xxxx_port_suspend to bool from int.
